TRIZ Business and Management V2 //halaman onboarding Next Get Started About Apps This application is a problem-solving application that implements the TRIZ problem-solving method introduced by Genrikh Saulovich Altshuller in a mobile form. Application Purpose This application is a learning media for users to learn and understand the triz method as one of the problem solving methods. The main purpose of this application is to facilitate users in learning and understanding the TRIZ method. In addition, users can also use this application to apply the TRIZ method in their daily lives. Main Feature In this application there is a feature that implements the TRIZ contradiction matrix in solving contradictory problems. There are also a number of materials on the basics of the TRIZ method that can help users to learn and understand the TRIZ method.
